      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it never stops. the doctors, the machines, the constant worry... and for what? she's still gone. i'm just so incredibly drained. i feel like i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even mean anything anymore. i honestly just want to sleep and not wake up. i just want the noise to stop.",
