      "content": "i know there are people to talk to, but i don't even have the energy to talk. like, what's the point of talking just to be told to \"keep going\" when i've already given everything i had? it feels like everything is just... empty. even the thought of tomorrow feels like a chore i can't finish. it just feels more logical to just let go than to keep fighting this emptiness.",
